'''Lords of Dismay [[Flightknife]]''' was a unit of [[Adumari]] [[Blade-32 superiority fighter]]s. They were the sixth Adumari unit to challenge [[Wedge Antilles/Legends|Wedge Antilles]]' [[Red Flight]] to a duel during Red Flight's test run on the Blade-32 Fighters.

During Red Flight's escape from the nation of [[Cartann]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Adumar/Legends|Adumar]], the Lords of Dismay and [[Strike the Moons Flightknife]] appeared, seemingly to finish off the badly damaged Red Flight. Suddenly, Strike the Moons fired upon them, justifying their action as refusing to allow "some honor-grubber" prevent Red Flight's escape.

